{"tid":2317936,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嶺南大學: 陳雲冷血涼薄，令人不齒 ; 保留追究他權利","createTime":"2020-12-09T03:15:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T03:15:28.000Z","uid":318316,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b039117f13814974f0b1ff607ec52c2785f4bb97","tid":2317936,"uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T03:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dm0SbNo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdm0SbNo.jpg&h=b6ec3d24&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n社交網發文嘲諷張竹君喪夫<br />\n陳雲上周日早上於（6日）於社交網站發文，點名談及張竹君丈夫再度病危，認為是「天行其道」、抗疫暴政擾民的報應，又指「禍福無門，唯人自召，善惡之報，如影隨行」。<br />\n<br />\n當晚，他再度發文回應張竹君丈夫病逝消息，指「皇天做事，陸續有來」，嘲諷「瘟君」一路炮製瘟疫害香港人執笠失業，害小孩失學，終於禍及其家，「一眾瘟君要死趁早，早死早着」。<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201208/TMQYK332OZALJPLMSDG6DL4FEM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201208%2FTMQYK332OZALJPLMSDG6DL4FEM%2F&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3W8o9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=a5910775\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201208%2FTMQYK332OZALJPLMSDG6DL4FEM%2F&h=59a495f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201208/TMQYK332OZALJPLMSDG6DL4FEM/</a>"}]}